name: Transport Buffer
description: On the first turn the user bounces into the air becoming uncontrollable and evades most attacks. Gust Twister Thunder and Sky Uppercut have normal accuracy against a mid-air Pokemon with Gust and Twister also gaining doubled power. The user may also be hit in mid-air if it was previously targeted by Lock-On or Mind Reader or if it is attacked by a Pokemon with No Guard. On the second turn the user descends and has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
